title: mattie
author: mattie
content: Hi,As fun for nostalgia I'm offering my old Butterfly labs ( 5GH japaleno) probably one of the first asic miner on the market for sale.It is still in perfect working order.Probably most people threw it in the trash long ago , but as miner there is some value in nostalgia on the times we got scammed by companies for a good reminder to us all when they didn't deliver as promise or even went bankrupt and didn't deliver our products.https://ibb.co/0DYv0DNLet's see how many people like nostalgia and bid awayÂ  .
